Author-Name: Joan Esteban  
Author-Name: Debraj Ray  
Title: Linking Conflict to Inequality and Polarization 
Abstract:
 In this paper we study a behavioral model of conflict that provides a
 basis for choosing certain indices of dispersion as indicators for
 conflict. We show that a suitable monotone transform of the equilibrium
 level of conflict can be proxied by a linear function of the Gini
 coefficient, the Herfindahl-Hirschman fractionalization index, and a
 specific measure of polarization due to Esteban and Ray. (JEL D31, D63,
 D74)
